{"tid":1954860,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想唔想TVB執笠？又有任務做喇","createTime":"2020-04-02T06:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T13:46:37.000Z","uid":65368,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82a97e3207c18c83e0da87476636dcfc47c065cb","tid":1954860,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"真係零成本就可以趕走廣告商，只係需要花你少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/413698682820320/posts/602842013905985/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F413698682820320%2Fposts%2F602842013905985%2F&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=89e8cbfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/413698682820320/posts/602842013905985/</a><br />\n<br />\n【萬寧退貨行動@2 Apr 20】<br />\n🚶🏻&zwj;♂️1. 去萬寧  🛒2. 買農本方產品  ♻️3. 退貨<br />\n📸4. 喺收銀處影退返嚟嘅錢，擺上FB  💌5. Email大大老細<br />\n.<br />\n👇🏻去農本方專頁留言👇🏻<br />\n農本方即溶沖劑<br />\n農本方 Nong's<br />\n農本方中醫診所<br />\n.<br />\n💡【行動目的】<br />\n1️⃣懲罰柒台大廣告商<br />\n2️⃣希望萬寧運用影響力，令各大品牌減少落TVB廣告<br />\n注：萬寧停咗TVB廣告，今次行動係針對品牌嘅廣告決策，長遠爭取萬寧出聲叫供應商唔好落TVB廣告！<br />\n.<br />\n🛒【退貨商品名單】<br />\n金靈芝、感冒沖劑-銀翹散、止咳沖劑、失眠沖劑<br />\n.<br />\n♻️【大家知唔知萬寧有14日退貨保證？】<br />\n顧客退款後貨品會被扔，供應商將被萬寧扣回銷售額！💸<br />\n即係如果多人退款供應商會蝕錢！🤪<br />\n退得愈多，蝕得愈多。😈<br />\n💢買貨時記住拎單，印花要退返<br />\n<br />\n小編親身測試🥳<br />\n買完即刻退得，隔幾日退亦得，得咗！<br />\n.<br />\n❓【農本方衰乜？】<br />\n農本方喺TVB播超長長長長長嘅廣告<br />\n農本方母公司：培力控股<br />\n💩老闆陳宇齡：貴州政協委員🇨🇳<br />\n💩中藥顆粒於廣西廠房製造🇨🇳<br />\n💩獨董陳建強 - 頭號梁粉🤮兼港台顧問委員會主席🤮，多次喺會議干預編採：<br />\n👎🏻「個人不支持港台直播民間記者會」<br />\n👎🏻「港台播放《願榮光歸香港》具爭議性」<br />\n👎🏻「應製作提升認識一國兩制和社會共融的節目」<br />\n👎🏻「《頭條新聞》有違「準確持平」準則」（明明係諷刺時事節目，節目名有&ldquo;新聞&rdquo;兩個字就夾硬話係新聞報道，必須持平）<br />\n對住咁極品嘅公司，我哋唔係唔行動呀嘛？🤪<br />\n.<br />\n【Source】<br />\n如何善用萬寧14日退貨保證？ - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/38cBFhm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38cBFhm&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=b36a71a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/38cBFhm</a><br />\n腦細係政協 - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2J1j7GO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2J1j7GO&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=6839ee72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2J1j7GO</a><br />\n打壓港台  - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UlcXXf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UlcXXf&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=a2646c03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UlcXXf</a> <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2x7RU2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2x7RU2I&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=8b925bdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2x7RU2I</a><br />\n頭條新聞係謠言？ - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2wkMt0e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wkMt0e&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=332401d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2wkMt0e</a><br />\n<br />\n#退貨行動 #農本方  #紅本方 #萬寧"},{"pid":"f4ac889cab31eac615b8f73aca3ace874bbd023d","tid":1954860,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70813c972f0e32ea37497d2d26fb5d5f2ad3ce8e","tid":1954860,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f05afa6b6220be1b325765718b34b3dbcbb11413","tid":1954860,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6d8fc544b5f392ce7e558d478d68d4352508218","tid":1954860,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e687f3645e41b267b988e9eb170f93198f0b4f9","tid":1954860,"uid":65368,"lik